data.description: Wonderfully convenient location in Kennesaw located close to luxury shopping, top restaurants, and recreational facilities. The nearby nature and dog park offers a plethora of hidden trailers for outdoor enthusiasts to explore. Come experience this quiet, peaceful, and friendly community that's a short drive from the world class amenities of cosmopolitan Atlanta, GA. Inside this home enjoy an open concept layout with an exceptionally open living room and ample natural light.
